Package: pressfreedom
Title: Press Freedom Dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Peter", "Baumgartner", , "petzi53@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4526-8791"))
Description: A Shiny dashboard for exploring Reporters Without Borders (RWB)
    Press Freedom Index data from 2002 to the present. Combines RWB scores
    with United Nations M49 geographic classifications to enable comparisons
    across countries, regions, and time.
